{"title":"Traditional South-Indian Mithai","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"kaju-pakam","title":"Bellam Kaju Pakam","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"pro-des-title pro-info-box\"\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eA delicate and rich treat\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eDadu’s Kaju Pakam is another traditional delicacy made to perfection, with authentic bellam\/jaggery\/gud preparation and the highest quality whole cashews. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOnline Kaju Pakam orders are fulfilled by our trusted and reputed logistics partners with complete safety precautions and delivered straight to your doorstep. Dadu's Kaju Pakam 1 kg price, Dadu's Kaju Pakam 500 gm price and Dadu's Kaju Pakam 250 gm price is the same as that of any of our retail outlets with no extra charges.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKaju Pakam can be bought online in an easy way via our website. Just add to cart, checkout, and get the delivery to enjoy this most sought after sweet.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"pro-description-box pro-info-box\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eShelf Life\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e30 days from packaging\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eIngredients\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCashew, Jaggery. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eStorage Instructions\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in a cool and dry place\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"500 g","offer_id":44691308347672,"sku":null,"price":1380.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"1 kg","offer_id":44691308380440,"sku":null,"price":2760.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/BellamKajuPakam_5.jpg?v=1779261802"},{"product_id":"ariselu","title":"Bellam Ariselu","description":"","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342289428760,"sku":null,"price":325.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"500 gms","offer_id":47862460121368,"sku":null,"price":650.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":47862460154136,"sku":null,"price":1300.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/BellamAriselu.jpg?v=1779261731"},{"product_id":"dryfruit-putharekulu","title":"Dryfruit Putharekulu","description":"\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWith Love From Andhra\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience the unique and exquisite taste of Dadu’s Dry fruit Pootharekulu, a beloved sweet from Andhra Pradesh. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEach piece is wrapped in a wafer-thin rice starch layer that resembles paper, stuffed generously with sugar, dry fruits, and nuts. This traditional treat, known for its delicate texture and rich filling, is perfect for festivals, religious occasions, and weddings. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCelebrate the timeless charm of Dadu's Putharekulu, a sweet that brings joy to every moment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAt Dadu's, we ensure that you can shop your favourite sweets online with ease.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadu's Dry Fruit Pootharekulu is delivered to your home with utmost care by our reliable logistics partners.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor international shipping inquiries, contact our support. Our clients within Hyderabad, India can get instant deliver